document_data.name: Harl Beskel
document_data.mainbody:
'''Harl Beskel''' was a [[half-orc]] [[rogue]] from [[Thesk]] who lived in [[Undumor|Emmech]] (later known as Undumor) around [[1374 DR]]. He purported to be a merchant but was spying on the fortress on behalf of [[Thay]].
